{
  "stem": "25178.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I had one customer who came in once.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had to develop a roll of film for him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had dressed himself in a Nazi uniform with a helmet, with a Swastika painted on it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when he came in, I told him I don't want to work for you no more.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, go someplace else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, this is no joke.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] Like my daughter told me that, last week she was walking with her baby and her husband on the street, and a well-dressed man walked by in the opposite direction.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my son, he wears a kippah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He's a very-- very orthodox religious, my son-in-law, and my daughter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when he passed them, he said-- he said to them, swine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My son-in-law, the only thing he said was, oh, really?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If it had been me, I don't know what I would have done.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told my wife the same thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I probably would have kicked him somewhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know, but I don't have to take that anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Never again.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I want to ask you if there was anything else that you'd like to add, perhaps something that we forgot or any incidences that you'd like to include in this tape?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There are so many instances of what happened in Westmalle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I recall one instance-- we had a terrible winter, and I had no coat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was a very tall man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they gave me his coat, which was much too big for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was hanging all the way to my shoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Winter coat.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
